---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AXSetrakb - Crypto Asset Tracking & Alternative Investment Analytics"
  description="Track cryptocurrency portfolios, manage alternative investments, monitor DeFi positions, and secure digital assets with advanced blockchain analytics tools."
  lang="en"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">AXSetrakb</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">AXSetrakb</Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Crypto Asset Tracking & Investment Analytics</h1>
    <p>Your comprehensive platform for cryptocurrency portfolio management, alternative investment tracking, DeFi analytics, and digital asset security.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Crypto Asset Tracking</h2>
      <p>Monitor your entire cryptocurrency portfolio across wallets and exchanges in real time. Track Bitcoin, Ethereum, altcoins, and tokens with live price feeds and performance analytics.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Portfolio Management</h2>
      <p>Consolidate traditional and digital assets in a single dashboard. Rebalance allocations, set alerts for price movements, and visualize your net worth across all asset classes.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Alternative Investments</h2>
      <p>Explore tokenized real estate, commodities, private equity, and NFT collectibles. Evaluate risk-adjusted returns and diversify beyond conventional markets.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>DeFi & Blockchain</h2>
      <p>Track yield farming positions, liquidity pools, staking rewards, and lending protocols. Stay informed on smart contract audits and emerging DeFi opportunities.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Digital Asset Security</h2>
      <p>Best practices for securing your crypto holdings with hardware wallets, multi-signature setups, and custody solutions. Protect against hacks, scams, and key loss.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Investment Analytics & Tools</h2>
      <p>Advanced charting, on-chain analysis, tax reporting tools, and AI-powered market insights. Make data-driven decisions with institutional-grade analytics.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>
